                <!-- display the comment text -->
                <div class='comment_text entry-content-wrapper clearfix'  itemprop="commentText" >
                <p>What about Nordic nRF905? Has anyone tried those? Those are Sub 1 GHz, and are rather cheap (2 for $13 on Amazon), have all the advantages of the nRF24L01+, plus a much longer working range.</p>
<p>I haven&#8217;t tried the nRF24L01+, but I&#8217;ve seen people claiming that, in practice, they only work for around 50-100 ft in open air.</p>
